data.name: SPECIAL FOLEY CATHETERS
data.description:
## COMPOSITION
- 100% Silicon and 100% Natural Rubber
- Lubricated Coating Layer

## STERILIZATION
- Ethylene Oxide (EO) Sterile

## PRESENTATIONS
- 100% Silicon (Latex Free) and 100% Natural Rubber (Latex)
- Hard Valve
- Color-Coded Size Identification

## PERFORMANCE
- Highly Slippery and Smooth Surface allowing successful introduction
- Central positioned Balloon
